information: SALEM-Frucht GmbH & Co. KG is a wholesaler of apples and pears near Lake Constance. The quality of our orchard fruits is extremely important to us, and for this reason, we are always personally and directly in contact with our growers. Our 250 fruit farmers work in accordance with the standards for integrated production, and are QS and EurepGap certified. The most important varieties of apple include Royal Gala, Braeburn, Jonagold, Elstar, Golden Delicious, Idared, CoxOrange, Rubinette, Boskoop and KIKU
